{"tid":1901844,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[一帶一路] 希臘比雷埃夫斯港郵輪碼頭擴建工程啟動","createTime":"2020-02-28T04:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T18:58:45.000Z","uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ab537fac0effe61e2dac45f83c8bcd55bbf03a","tid":1901844,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:52:06.000Z","msg":"希臘比雷埃夫斯港（以下簡稱&ldquo;比港&rdquo;）郵輪碼頭擴建工程開工儀式25日在比雷埃夫斯市古董。擴建項目包括新建2個郵輪深水泊位，建成後新泊位可靠泊目前全球最大的長360米，載客量6000人的郵輪。<br />\n<br />\n中遠海運比雷埃夫斯港口有限公司董事長俞曾港介紹，擴建項目在2023年完成後，將鞏固比港在地中海郵輪產業中的母港分區，進一步帶動希臘旅遊經濟發展。<br />\n<br />\n希臘海洋和島嶼政策部長揚尼斯&middot;普拉基奧塔基斯在儀式上說，比港郵輪碼頭擴建是提升比港碼頭競爭力的重要替代。希臘有決心，有信心將比港打造成地中海地區最大的郵輪港口。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐希臘大使章啟月在接受新華社記者採訪時表示，項目在短時間內逐步動工，得到了希臘社會各界高度肯定。她相信，中希雙方不斷在港口發展，旅遊及服務貿易等方面的合作將取得新進展。<br />\n<br />\n2016年4月，中遠海運收購比港港務局67％的股權，同年8月開始接手手港務局經營業務。2019年10月，希臘港口和發展規劃委員會批准了比港港務局提交的港口發展規劃，該規劃投資總額約6億歐元（1歐元約合1.1美元）。<br />\n<br />\n中共係地中海又多個軍用碼頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b21751ad59e59bfceaecf026d0ab291b4f6043","tid":1901844,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:53:30.000Z","msg":"SOURCE: 支那新華社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-02/26/c_138818897.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Fenglish%2F2020-02%2F26%2Fc_138818897.htm&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0R0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=be38933d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-02/26/c_138818897.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a62cd6458c41ed06c961c60e7135d0ad49612bb4","tid":1901844,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ce4b1b12c206eed1c2abf90bae6142329424bd","tid":1901844,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0923ed4db76fc7dd92c46f142675bf824726cf9c","tid":1901844,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"專搞三線國家"},{"pid":"c80c0eca5d1400013907a6e886a939933739d081","tid":1901844,"uid":222392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"方便法西支派兵登陸歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f52bea889b22719b34cff5d63e3afe1f57dc5c3","tid":1901844,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c80c0eca5d1400013907a6e886a939933739d081","tid":1901844,"uid":222392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"方便法西支派兵登陸歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"非洲中亞歐洲太平洋都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa599587f4d127ad72a93d06e502ffb1a7a6268","tid":1901844,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0923ed4db76fc7dd92c46f142675bf824726cf9c","tid":1901844,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"專搞三線國家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"唔親支點復活"},{"pid":"f738d1ab80f0bc2b10a5a5616676127fda57fd2b","tid":1901844,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T18:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]